{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Mockingbirds are badass."}]},{"cues":[{"time":3000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":4000,"text":"They are."},{"time":6000,"text":"Mockingbirds -- that's Mimus polyglottos --"},{"time":8000,"text":"are the emcees of the animal kingdom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10000,"text":"They listen and mimic and remix what they like."},{"time":12000,"text":"They rock the mic outside my window every morning."},{"time":14000,"text":"I can hear them sing the sounds of the car alarms"},{"time":17000,"text":"like they were songs of spring."},{"time":19000,"text":"I mean, if you can talk it, a mockingbird can squawk it."},{"time":21000,"text":"So check it, I'm gonna to catch mockingbirds."},{"time":23000,"text":"I'm going to trap mockingbirds all across the nation"},{"time":26000,"text":"and put them gently into mason jars like mockingbird Molotov cocktails."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"Yeah. And as I drive through a neighborhood,"},{"time":32000,"text":"say, where people got-a-lotta, I'll take a mockingbird I caught"},{"time":35000,"text":"in a neighborhood where folks ain't got nada and just let it go, you know."},{"time":38000,"text":"Up goes the bird, out come the words, \"Juanito, Juanito,"},{"time":41000,"text":"vente a comer mi hijo!\""},{"time":43000,"text":"Oh, I'm going to be the Johnny Appleseed of sound."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"Cruising random city streets, rocking a drop-top Cadillac"},{"time":50000,"text":"with a big backseat, packing like 13 brown paper Walmart bags"},{"time":53000,"text":"full of loaded mockingbirds, and I'll get everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"I'll get the nitwit on the network news saying,"},{"time":59000,"text":"\"We'll be back in a moment with more on the crisis.\""},{"time":61000,"text":"I'll get some asshole at a watering hole asking what brand the ice is."},{"time":63000,"text":"I'll get that lady at the laundromat who always seems to know what being nice is."},{"time":66000,"text":"I'll get your postman making dinner plans."},{"time":69000,"text":"I'll get the last time you lied."},{"time":71000,"text":"I'll get, \"Baby, just give me the frickin' TV guide.\""},{"time":73000,"text":"I'll get a lonely, little sentence with real error in it,"},{"time":75000,"text":"\"Yeah, I guess I could come inside, but only for a minute.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"I'll get an ESL class in Chinatown learning \"It's Raining, It's Pouring.\""},{"time":82000,"text":"I'll put a mockingbird on a late-night train just to get an old man snoring."},{"time":85000,"text":"I'll get your ex-lover telling someone else, \"Good morning.\""},{"time":88000,"text":"I'll get everyone's good mornings."},{"time":90000,"text":"I don't care how you make 'em."},{"time":92000,"text":"Aloha. Konichiwa. Shalom. Ah-Salam Alaikum."},{"time":95000,"text":"Everybody means everybody, means everybody here."},{"time":97000,"text":"And so maybe I'll build a gilded cage."},{"time":99000,"text":"I'll line the bottom with old notebook pages."},{"time":101000,"text":"Inside it, I will place a mockingbird for --"},{"time":104000,"text":"short explanation, hippie parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"What does a violin have to do with technology?"},{"time":110000,"text":"Where in the world is this world heading?"},{"time":112000,"text":"On one end, gold bars --"},{"time":115000,"text":"on the other, an entire planet."},{"time":117000,"text":"We are 12 billion light years from the edge."},{"time":120000,"text":"That's a guess."},{"time":121000,"text":"Space is length and breadth continued indefinitely,"},{"time":124000,"text":"but you cannot buy a ticket to travel commercially to space in America"},{"time":127000,"text":"because countries are beginning to eat like us, live like us and die like us."},{"time":130000,"text":"You might wanna avert your gaze, because that"},{"time":132000,"text":"is a newt about to regenerate its limb,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and shaking hands spreads more germs than kissing."},{"time":138000,"text":"There's about 10 million phage per job."},{"time":140000,"text":"It's a very strange world inside a nanotube."},{"time":143000,"text":"Women can talk; black men ski; white men build strong buildings;"},{"time":147000,"text":"we build strong suns."},{"time":149000,"text":"The surface of the Earth is absolutely riddled with holes,"},{"time":152000,"text":"and here we are, right in the middle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"It is the voice of life that calls us to come and learn."},{"time":160000,"text":"When all the little mockingbirds fly away,"},{"time":162000,"text":"they're going to sound like the last four days."},{"time":165000,"text":"I will get uptown gurus, downtown teachers,"},{"time":168000,"text":"broke-ass artists and dealers, and Filipino preachers, leaf blowers,"},{"time":171000,"text":"bartenders, boob-job doctors, hooligans, garbage men,"},{"time":173000,"text":"your local Congressmen in the spotlight, guys in the overhead helicopters."},{"time":175000,"text":"Everybody gets heard."},{"time":177000,"text":"Everybody gets this one, honest mockingbird as a witness."},{"time":181000,"text":"And I'm on this."},{"time":183000,"text":"I'm on this 'til the whole thing spreads,"},{"time":185000,"text":"with chat rooms and copycats and moms maybe tucking kids into bed"},{"time":187000,"text":"singing, \"Hush, little baby, don't say a word."},{"time":190000,"text":"Wait for the man with the mockingbird.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"Yeah. And then come the news crews, and"},{"time":196000,"text":"the man-in-the-street interviews, and the letters to the editor."},{"time":198000,"text":"Everybody asking, just who is responsible for this citywide,"},{"time":201000,"text":"nationwide mockingbird cacophony, and somebody finally is going to tip"},{"time":204000,"text":"the City Council of Monterey, California off to me,"},{"time":207000,"text":"and they'll offer me a key to the city."},{"time":209000,"text":"A gold-plated, oversized key to the city"},{"time":211000,"text":"and that is all I need, 'cause if I get that, I can unlock the air."},{"time":215000,"text":"I'll listen for what's missing, and I'll put it there."},{"time":219000,"text":"Thank you, TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"Chris Anderson: Wow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"Wow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}